snippet.title: Deathverse -Let it Die- - State of Play Oct 2021 Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Presenting the multiplayer melee survival action game ""DEATHVERSE -LET IT DIE-”!

Greetings to all of you looking to relieve your daily stress and fulfill an insane desire for extreme self-expression. 

We invite you to take part as a contestant in a literal survival game show that has enthralled the world over! !
